1
00:00:22,689 --> 00:00:26,026
Kau tahu kenapa aku memilih mereka?

2
00:00:29,946 --> 00:00:33,783
Kenapa aku memilih mereka
untuk membentuk semula dunia ini?

3
00:00:34,617 --> 00:00:37,954
Sebab mereka lemah.

4
00:00:39,456 --> 00:00:41,916
Mudah dipatahkan.

5
00:00:44,961 --> 00:00:46,963
Mudah dibentuk semula.

6
00:00:47,589 --> 00:00:49,049
Mudah dikawal.

7
00:00:51,217 --> 00:00:53,803
Wadah yang sempurna.

8
00:00:57,891 --> 00:00:59,059
Sayang.

9
00:00:59,142 --> 00:01:00,977
- Mak.
- Aduhai, sayang.

10
00:01:01,061 --> 00:01:03,772
Mak tak faham. Macam mana kamu…

11
00:01:03,855 --> 00:01:04,898
Dia ahli sihir.

12
00:01:04,981 --> 00:01:07,108
Ahli sihir sebenar.

13
00:01:07,192 --> 00:01:08,234
Mike.

14
00:01:10,361 --> 00:01:11,404
Kau berjaya.

15
00:01:11,488 --> 00:01:12,781
Kau berjaya buat.

16
00:01:15,617 --> 00:01:16,534
Budak-budak itu.

17
00:01:16,618 --> 00:01:18,787
Vecna dapat tangkap budak-budak itu.

18
00:01:18,870 --> 00:01:21,081
Aku tahu. Derek, Mary, Glenn.

19
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:24,417
Tak. Bukan mereka saja.

20
00:01:26,544 --> 00:01:29,380
Yang lain pun
tak sempat keluar dari Hawkins.

21
00:01:31,049 --> 00:01:34,594
Aku boleh tolong lawan
kalau aku bertindak lebih awal.

22
00:01:36,346 --> 00:01:37,388
Tapi aku lambat.

23
00:01:38,765 --> 00:01:40,725
Sekarang dia dah tangkap mereka.

24
00:01:42,143 --> 00:01:43,394
Kesemua 12.

25
00:01:45,980 --> 00:01:47,107
Kita gagal.

26
00:01:48,650 --> 00:01:49,567
Saya gagal.

27
00:01:49,651 --> 00:01:50,485
Tidak.

28
00:01:56,199 --> 00:01:57,951
Terowong. Radio Shack.

29
00:02:47,041 --> 00:02:51,337
Mungkin kamu tak ingat sangat
macam mana kamu boleh ada di sini.

30
00:02:52,338 --> 00:02:53,339
- Mary!
- Keliru.

31
00:02:53,423 --> 00:02:54,340
Holly!

32
00:02:54,424 --> 00:02:56,968
Raksasa-raksasa itu cuba tangkap kamu.

33
00:02:57,051 --> 00:02:57,927
Hai!

34
00:02:58,511 --> 00:03:00,305
Tapi saya sempat selamatkan.

35
00:03:00,388 --> 00:03:01,764
- Apa khabar?
- Baik.

36
00:03:01,848 --> 00:03:02,849
Tempat ini,

37
00:03:03,474 --> 00:03:04,475
rumah saya,

38
00:03:05,101 --> 00:03:06,603
rumah kamu juga sekarang.

39
00:03:07,187 --> 00:03:08,354
Tempat berlindung.

40
00:03:08,938 --> 00:03:11,774
Asalkan tak pergi
ke hutan yang dipenuhi raksasa,

41
00:03:11,858 --> 00:03:13,484
kamu selamat di sini.

42
00:03:13,568 --> 00:03:16,571
Saya tahu ramai antara kamu
yang tertanya-tanya,

43
00:03:16,654 --> 00:03:19,574
bila kawan-kawan
dan keluarga kamu akan datang?

44
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:24,245
Tapi banyak lagi dalam taruhan
selain nyawa insan yang kamu sayang.

45
00:03:26,289 --> 00:03:27,999
Saya tak nak buat kamu takut.

46
00:03:28,833 --> 00:03:31,502
Tapi kamu cukup berani
untuk tahu hal sebenar.

47
00:03:32,086 --> 00:03:35,632
Kegelapan jahat sedang merebak
bukan saja di Hawkins,

48
00:03:35,715 --> 00:03:36,925
malah seluruh dunia.

49
00:03:37,008 --> 00:03:40,011
Tak lama lagi, ia takkan dapat dihentikan.

50
00:03:40,637 --> 00:03:44,849
Anggaplah kegelapan ini
macam Black Thing dalam buku kamu.

51
00:03:44,933 --> 00:03:49,270
Kegelapan ini ugut keluarga kamu
macam Black Thing ugut keluarga Meg, tapi,

52
00:03:49,354 --> 00:03:52,190
saya dah jumpa cara
untuk tewaskan kegelapan ini.

53
00:03:52,273 --> 00:03:53,483
Macam mana?

54
00:03:55,109 --> 00:03:59,530
Saya mengembara jauh
ke luar dimensi kita buat masa yang lama.

55
00:04:00,114 --> 00:04:02,742
Dalam kembara itu,
saya menemukan dunia lain.

56
00:04:03,701 --> 00:04:05,245
Dunia yang jauh dari Bumi.

57
00:04:05,328 --> 00:04:08,706
Dunia itu serupa dengan dunia kita, tapi,

58
00:04:09,582 --> 00:04:10,708
semuanya baik-baik.

59
00:04:11,459 --> 00:04:13,294
Tak ada raksasa dan kegelapan.

60
00:04:14,712 --> 00:04:15,838
Hanya ada cahaya.

61
00:04:16,422 --> 00:04:19,342
Inilah sebab sebenar kamu semua dipilih.

62
00:04:19,842 --> 00:04:20,760
Kamu…

63
00:04:21,511 --> 00:04:23,263
tak seperti budak-budak lain.

64
00:04:23,846 --> 00:04:26,057
Macam Meg juga, kamu istimewa.

65
00:04:27,058 --> 00:04:29,060
Kamu ada kuasa terpendam di sini.

66
00:04:30,228 --> 00:04:33,940
Sekiranya kita bekerjasama,
kita boleh membangkitkan kuasa itu,

67
00:04:34,023 --> 00:04:37,193
menyalurkan tenaga kita
dan menarik dunia baharu itu.

68
00:04:37,277 --> 00:04:38,903
Apabila cahaya itu

69
00:04:40,405 --> 00:04:41,781
mendatangi kegelapan,

70
00:04:42,365 --> 00:04:44,117
kegelapan akan terhapus,

71
00:04:44,701 --> 00:04:47,120
insan tersayang akan selamat, dan kamu…

72
00:04:49,289 --> 00:04:50,623
Kamu akan jadi wira.

73
00:04:55,378 --> 00:04:56,963
Ya, Holly?

74
00:04:57,755 --> 00:05:00,091
Awak akan keluar lagi?

75
00:05:01,009 --> 00:05:03,594
Untuk bawa budak istimewa lain ke sini?

76
00:05:03,678 --> 00:05:05,972
Kasihan Holly. Dia pertama dipilih.

77
00:05:06,889 --> 00:05:08,850
Dia ditinggalkan seorang diri.

78
00:05:08,933 --> 00:05:11,644
Tapi jangan risau.
Saya takkan tinggalkan kamu.

79
00:05:12,395 --> 00:05:14,063
Tinggalkan sesiapa pun lagi.

80
00:05:14,147 --> 00:05:15,648
Tapi buat masa sekarang,

81
00:05:16,190 --> 00:05:18,484
makan dan main puas-puas.

82
00:05:19,610 --> 00:05:21,362
Paling penting, berehat.

83
00:05:22,405 --> 00:05:23,489
Sebab esok?

84
00:05:25,783 --> 00:05:27,160
Esok, ia akan bermula.

85
00:06:31,641 --> 00:06:38,648
BABAK LIMA: OPERASI KEJUTAN

86
00:07:01,379 --> 00:07:02,880
Kata tak ada yang keluar?

87
00:07:02,964 --> 00:07:04,966
Unit Keselamatan sendiri kata.

88
00:07:05,049 --> 00:07:06,843
Mereka lesap macam Houdini?

89
00:07:06,926 --> 00:07:07,969
Saya tak tahu, tuan.

90
00:07:08,052 --> 00:07:10,054
Periksa setiap ceruk bangunan ini.

91
00:07:10,138 --> 00:07:14,225
Setiap bilik, lubang dan panel akses.
Mari pergi. Gerak. Gerak!

92
00:07:51,971 --> 00:07:52,972
Awak okey tak?

93
00:07:53,055 --> 00:07:55,224
Ia dah hilang.

94
00:07:56,184 --> 00:07:57,477
Kita terlalu jauh.

95
00:07:57,560 --> 00:08:00,855
Tak apa. Kita dah cukup jauh.
Mereka takkan dapat kejar.

96
00:08:00,938 --> 00:08:02,482
Hebat betul helah kamu.

97
00:08:03,608 --> 00:08:06,402
Sekejap, mungkin saya patut kata "gempak".

98
00:08:07,153 --> 00:08:09,655
Kamu yang ajar El perkataan itu, bukan?

99
00:08:10,239 --> 00:08:13,367
Saya bawa pengaruh tak baik.

100
00:08:13,451 --> 00:08:15,703
Ya, samalah kita.

101
00:08:30,927 --> 00:08:32,678
- Lucas?
- Aduhai.

102
00:08:32,762 --> 00:08:34,514
- Tidak.
- Hei, semua.

103
00:08:34,597 --> 00:08:35,598
Tidak.

104
00:08:36,849 --> 00:08:37,683
Alamak.

105
00:08:37,767 --> 00:08:39,060
Calar sikit saja.

106
00:08:39,143 --> 00:08:41,395
- Alat pertolongan cemas.
- Alamak!

107
00:08:41,479 --> 00:08:43,105
Sekejap.

108
00:08:43,189 --> 00:08:44,899
- Boleh angkat? Tunjuk.
- Ya.

109
00:08:48,110 --> 00:08:49,820
Taklah teruk sangat.

110
00:08:49,904 --> 00:08:50,947
Aduh.

111
00:08:51,030 --> 00:08:55,159
Ya, baru nampak ganas nanti
kalau ada parut macam itu.

112
00:08:55,243 --> 00:08:57,370
Maaf sebab gagal melindungi mereka.

113
00:08:57,453 --> 00:09:01,290
Kau dah cuba sedaya upaya.
Kau lawan. Kau bahayakan nyawa kau.

114
00:09:01,374 --> 00:09:02,416
Padu ayunan kau.

115
00:09:04,293 --> 00:09:05,294
Kau nampak?

116
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:07,213
Bukan setakat nampak.

117
00:09:09,298 --> 00:09:14,303
Jadi, Demo terapung,
tangan dan kaki patah, kemudian mati.

118
00:09:14,387 --> 00:09:16,389
Itu semua kerja kau?

119
00:09:16,472 --> 00:09:19,141
Ya, begitulah.

120
00:09:19,225 --> 00:09:20,309
Gilalah.

121
00:09:21,727 --> 00:09:22,853
Gilalah.

122
00:09:23,437 --> 00:09:27,942
Kau tahu apa maknanya, bukan?
Kau betul-betul macam Will Yang Bijaksana.

123
00:09:28,025 --> 00:09:30,778
- Tak juga.
- Dia ahli sihir, bukan ahli jampi.

124
00:09:30,861 --> 00:09:33,197
Okey. Ya, mungkinlah.

125
00:09:33,281 --> 00:09:35,241
Tapi kau faham maksud aku, bukan?

126
00:09:35,324 --> 00:09:37,702
Ini betul-betul mengubah keadaan.

127
00:09:37,785 --> 00:09:39,120
Kita ada El kedua.

128
00:09:39,203 --> 00:09:41,998
Aku bukan El kedua. Aku tak ada kuasa.

129
00:09:42,081 --> 00:09:44,917
Aku cuma menyedut, mencuri kuasa Vecna.

130
00:09:45,001 --> 00:09:47,461
Aku perlu dekat dengan minda sarang.

131
00:09:47,545 --> 00:09:48,879
Vecna takkan kembali.

132
00:09:48,963 --> 00:09:51,048
- Tapi Demo mungkin kembali.
- Tak.

133
00:09:51,132 --> 00:09:53,259
Mereka dah dapat budak-budak itu,

134
00:09:53,342 --> 00:09:55,177
jadi dia dah ada wadahnya.

135
00:09:59,724 --> 00:10:00,725
"Wadah"?

136
00:10:00,808 --> 00:10:03,144
Dia panggil mereka wadah.

137
00:10:03,227 --> 00:10:06,147
Dia cakap,
"Wadah untuk membentuk semula dunia."

138
00:10:06,230 --> 00:10:08,190
Aku cuma harap teori kau salah.

139
00:10:09,108 --> 00:10:10,026
Teori apa?

140
00:10:10,943 --> 00:10:12,069
6 November.

141
00:10:13,321 --> 00:10:14,989
Hari semua ini bermula

142
00:10:16,490 --> 00:10:17,742
ialah hari ia berakhir.

143
00:10:22,538 --> 00:10:23,372
Kau okey?

144
00:10:28,753 --> 00:10:31,464
Okey, Lucas. Perlahan-lahan.

145
00:10:31,964 --> 00:10:33,466
Pegang tangan aku.

146
00:10:35,134 --> 00:10:36,802
Tahan sikit. Selangkah lagi.

147
00:10:36,886 --> 00:10:38,971
Hei. Mari sini.

148
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:44,894
Ada cara tak untuk berhubung
dengan minda sarang sekali lagi

149
00:10:44,977 --> 00:10:46,604
dan akses kuasa dia semula?

150
00:10:46,687 --> 00:10:48,439
Mustahil, melainkan…

151
00:10:48,522 --> 00:10:50,483
Sarang itu dekat. Mak tahu.

152
00:10:51,192 --> 00:10:54,737
Tapi kejadian tadi pun
kita sangka mustahil sebelum ini.

153
00:10:54,820 --> 00:10:55,821
Mak.

154
00:10:56,364 --> 00:10:57,990
Maksud mak, mungkin…

155
00:10:58,074 --> 00:11:00,201
Mungkin kali ini,

156
00:11:00,284 --> 00:11:02,828
jangan guna kuasa untuk lawan tentera dia.

157
00:11:02,912 --> 00:11:04,622
Guna kuasa untuk lawan dia.

158
00:11:04,705 --> 00:11:06,499
Lawan Vecna.

159
00:11:06,582 --> 00:11:08,668
Tikam dia dengan pedangnya sendiri.

160
00:11:08,751 --> 00:11:10,878
Kamu tak gagal malam ini.

161
00:11:11,921 --> 00:11:13,214
Apa yang kamu buat

162
00:11:14,131 --> 00:11:16,133
betul-betul luar biasa.

163
00:11:16,967 --> 00:11:18,761
Kamu sendiri yang cakap.

164
00:11:18,844 --> 00:11:22,431
Vecna pilih kamu
sebab dia pandang rendah kamu.

165
00:11:23,057 --> 00:11:25,476
Kami semua pandang rendah. Lagi-lagi mak.

166
00:11:25,559 --> 00:11:29,563
Itu satu kesilapan
yang mak takkan sekali-kali buat lagi.

167
00:11:30,231 --> 00:11:33,651
Tapi mak berani bertaruh
yang dia akan buat silap itu lagi.

168
00:11:33,734 --> 00:11:35,319
Apabila ia berlaku,

169
00:11:35,403 --> 00:11:39,573
itulah kesilapan terakhir
yang anak haram itu akan buat.

170
00:11:53,462 --> 00:11:56,132
Ajaib betul mereka kembali dengan selamat.

171
00:11:57,049 --> 00:12:01,470
Malangnya Bimmer mahal Harrington
tak dapat diselamatkan.

172
00:12:02,805 --> 00:12:04,557
Awak nak buat macam ini?

173
00:12:05,057 --> 00:12:07,309
Buat lawak macam tak ada apa-apa jadi?

174
00:12:11,856 --> 00:12:14,316
Rancangannya, awak cari Vecna dan balik.

175
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:16,444
- Tapi awak ada rancangan lain.
- Taklah.

176
00:12:16,527 --> 00:12:17,695
Tipu.

177
00:12:17,778 --> 00:12:19,613
Macam pasal masa latihan saya.

178
00:12:19,697 --> 00:12:23,659
Awak tak nak saya ikut menyusup
sebab awak nak bunuh Vecna dan mati.

179
00:12:23,743 --> 00:12:27,371
Hei, dengar sini.
Kejadian hari ini berbeza.

180
00:12:27,455 --> 00:12:30,958
Kamu tak mampu lawan Kryptonite.
Saya tak ada pilihan lain.

181
00:12:31,041 --> 00:12:32,001
Bom itu pula?

182
00:12:32,668 --> 00:12:35,504
Bom itu cuma langkah berjaga-jaga.

183
00:12:35,588 --> 00:12:38,340
Langkah berjaga-jaga
yang orang lain tak tahu.

184
00:12:40,217 --> 00:12:42,136
Saya nampak mata awak tadi.

185
00:12:43,679 --> 00:12:44,805
Saya nampak.

186
00:12:46,223 --> 00:12:48,100
Awak memang rancang nak mati.

187
00:12:51,187 --> 00:12:52,646
Sejak awal lagi.

188
00:12:55,733 --> 00:12:56,734
Hei!

189
00:12:57,359 --> 00:12:59,820
Kawan awak sepatutnya di sini, bukan?

190
00:13:12,166 --> 00:13:13,834
Aduhai, tolonglah.

191
00:13:31,936 --> 00:13:33,687
Cerah harapan kita nampaknya.

192
00:13:33,771 --> 00:13:34,939
Kita di lobi.

193
00:13:35,564 --> 00:13:39,318
Sebenarnya, kita nak ke mana?

194
00:13:39,401 --> 00:13:42,780
Itulah. Apa benda yang kita cari?

195
00:13:42,863 --> 00:13:44,448
Tengok Return of the Jedi?

196
00:13:44,532 --> 00:13:46,242
- Ada beruang teddy?
- Ewok.

197
00:13:46,325 --> 00:13:47,535
Terbaik dalam francais.

198
00:13:47,618 --> 00:13:48,452
- Yakah?
- Ya?

199
00:13:48,536 --> 00:13:51,163
Tak, tapi semua budak suka. Tak hairanlah.

200
00:13:51,247 --> 00:13:54,875
Dalam filem itu, pemberontak perlu
musnahkan Death Star kedua,

201
00:13:54,959 --> 00:13:59,046
tapi ada perisai tenaga pelindung
yang dicipta oleh penjana perisai.

202
00:13:59,129 --> 00:14:02,299
Susah-susah saja jelaskan filem
yang kami dah tengok.

203
00:14:02,383 --> 00:14:04,468
Yang peliknya, filem itu relevan.

204
00:14:05,052 --> 00:14:09,515
Aku rasa tembok daging bulat ini
sebenarnya perisai tenaga versi Vecna,

205
00:14:09,598 --> 00:14:11,267
cuma ia bukan fiksyen sains.

206
00:14:11,350 --> 00:14:15,354
Ini kuasa ghaib
yang dicipta oleh sihir gelap Vecna.

207
00:14:15,437 --> 00:14:19,567
Perisai sihir ini yang halang kita masuk
dan selamatkan Holly.

208
00:14:19,650 --> 00:14:23,028
Kalau betul kiraan aku,
penjananya ada di makmal ini.

209
00:14:23,112 --> 00:14:26,407
Jadi, kalau kita jumpa
penjana perisai sihir gelap itu…

210
00:14:26,490 --> 00:14:28,617
- Musnahkan tembok.
- Cari Vecna, selamatkan Holly.

211
00:14:28,701 --> 00:14:29,702
Pingat untuk semua.

212
00:14:29,785 --> 00:14:31,370
Macam mana rupa benda itu?

213
00:14:31,453 --> 00:14:33,163
Manalah aku tahu.

214
00:14:49,138 --> 00:14:50,139
Atas atau bawah?

215
00:14:51,223 --> 00:14:53,934
Dua-dua. Berpecah.
Dapat periksa banyak tempat.

216
00:14:54,018 --> 00:14:57,062
Ya, saya tak kisah,
tapi boleh kita tukar pasukan?

217
00:14:57,146 --> 00:14:58,856
Nance, kita berdua naik?

218
00:14:58,939 --> 00:15:00,482
- Saya…
- Kau seriuslah?

219
00:15:00,566 --> 00:15:02,276
Kami perlukan ruang.

220
00:15:02,359 --> 00:15:03,193
- Ya.
- Tolonglah.

221
00:15:03,277 --> 00:15:04,486
Baik. Kita berdua?

222
00:15:04,570 --> 00:15:05,905
Kita pun perlu ruang.

223
00:15:05,988 --> 00:15:08,616
Semua tak boleh kecuali Nancy.
Senang betul.

224
00:15:09,116 --> 00:15:11,368
Hei, kita tak ada masa.

225
00:15:11,452 --> 00:15:13,120
Ikut pasukan biasa saja.

226
00:15:13,203 --> 00:15:14,538
- Tak boleh…
- Saya…

227
00:15:14,622 --> 00:15:15,456
Muktamad.

228
00:15:18,459 --> 00:15:19,668
Bagus.

229
00:15:22,963 --> 00:15:24,173
Bagus sangat.

230
00:15:42,733 --> 00:15:44,777
Aku kejar kau!

231
00:15:49,949 --> 00:15:50,991
Jadi!

232
00:15:52,451 --> 00:15:53,869
Aku kejar kau!

233
00:15:54,703 --> 00:15:57,164
Tak adil betul kau sampai sehari awal.

234
00:15:57,247 --> 00:16:00,834
Macam mana? Aku tak tahulah.
Hijau sesuai tak dengan aku?

235
00:16:02,544 --> 00:16:04,421
Ya, sesuai sangat.

236
00:16:05,631 --> 00:16:07,800
- Apa masalahnya?
- Tak ada apa-apa.

237
00:16:07,883 --> 00:16:09,176
Kau nampak pelik.

238
00:16:09,259 --> 00:16:10,344
Aku rasa…

239
00:16:11,011 --> 00:16:13,555
Aku terlebih makan kek agaknya.

240
00:16:13,639 --> 00:16:16,183
Mungkin En. Whatsit ada teh?

241
00:16:16,266 --> 00:16:18,310
Mesti ada. Dia ada semua benda.

242
00:16:39,915 --> 00:16:41,500
- Kenapa datang?
- Ada hal.

243
00:16:41,583 --> 00:16:44,086
- Awak sepatutnya…
- Tunggu Henry keluar.

244
00:16:44,169 --> 00:16:46,463
Tapi dia cakap benda yang menyeramkan.

245
00:16:46,547 --> 00:16:50,426
- Ada orang nampak awak?
- Tak, saya hati-hati. Dengarlah dulu.

246
00:16:50,509 --> 00:16:51,969
Henry culik kami

247
00:16:52,052 --> 00:16:53,679
sebab dia nak gunakan kami

248
00:16:53,762 --> 00:16:56,640
untuk tarik dunia lain
ke dunia kita, Bumi.

249
00:16:56,724 --> 00:16:59,018
"Tarik dunia lain"? Saya tak fahamlah.

250
00:16:59,101 --> 00:17:02,771
Henry kata nak selamatkan Bumi.
Saya rasa dia nak hancurkannya.

251
00:17:02,855 --> 00:17:05,107
Apa-apa pun dia rancang, esok harinya.

252
00:17:05,190 --> 00:17:07,317
Kita perlu keluar dari Camazotz.

253
00:17:07,401 --> 00:17:08,277
Takkan sempat.

254
00:17:08,360 --> 00:17:10,279
Sebaik dia sedar awak tak ada,

255
00:17:10,362 --> 00:17:12,740
dia akan tangkap kita dengan kuasa dia.

256
00:17:15,117 --> 00:17:17,161
- Betul tak ada orang nampak?
- Ya.

257
00:17:30,340 --> 00:17:31,341
Kau siapa?

258
00:17:31,425 --> 00:17:32,760
Derek. Kau siapa?

259
00:17:32,843 --> 00:17:34,636
Apa kau buat di sini, bangang?

260
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:37,222
Aku bukan Derek Bangang. Aku Derek Baik.

261
00:17:37,306 --> 00:17:38,474
- Dengar semua?
- Tak.

262
00:17:38,557 --> 00:17:42,019
Cuma pasal kamu tak boleh lari
sebab tunggu Henry keluar.

263
00:17:42,102 --> 00:17:44,438
Takut dia cari kamu dengan sihir Vecna.

264
00:17:44,521 --> 00:17:46,774
Aku tak sebut "Vecna". Mana kau tahu?

265
00:17:46,857 --> 00:17:48,317
- Mike.
- Mike?

266
00:17:48,400 --> 00:17:49,234
Abang aku?

267
00:17:49,318 --> 00:17:52,071
- Dia kawan baik aku.
- Kau kawan baik Mike?

268
00:17:52,154 --> 00:17:55,199
Will, Lucas, Erica,
Pn. Byers dan Cik Robin juga.

269
00:17:55,282 --> 00:17:58,994
Kami gagal selamatkan yang lain.
Aku tak percaya orang di sini.

270
00:17:59,078 --> 00:18:02,915
Aku nampak muka kau tadi.
Aku fikir, "Holly tahu dia temberang."

271
00:18:02,998 --> 00:18:06,335
Jadi, aku ekori kau ke hutan.
Memang betul sangkaan aku.

272
00:18:06,418 --> 00:18:07,419
Boleh aku ikut?

273
00:18:07,503 --> 00:18:10,798
Tak! Kita takkan ke mana-mana
selagi Henry memerhati.

274
00:18:11,548 --> 00:18:13,217
Kalau alihkan perhatian dia?

275
00:18:14,259 --> 00:18:15,803
Kau tak boleh ikut kami.

276
00:18:17,054 --> 00:18:19,264
Tapi kau boleh tolong kami lari.

277
00:18:19,348 --> 00:18:24,228
Cuma tolonglah,
kau tak boleh jadi Derek Baik,

278
00:18:24,311 --> 00:18:27,815
sebab cara ini cuma akan menjadi
kalau kau Derek Bangang.

279
00:18:32,069 --> 00:18:34,029
Okey, matlamatnya mudah.

280
00:18:34,113 --> 00:18:36,323
Bawa Will dekat dengan minda sarang.

281
00:18:36,406 --> 00:18:40,035
Sebaik saja dia dah dekat,
dia berhubung semula.

282
00:18:40,119 --> 00:18:42,371
Kali ini, dia takkan serang Demo.

283
00:18:42,454 --> 00:18:44,081
Dia serang Vecna.

284
00:18:44,623 --> 00:18:47,584
Tumbangkan dia, tamatkan riwayat dia

285
00:18:47,668 --> 00:18:50,295
dan bala tenteranya
untuk akhiri bencana ini.

286
00:18:51,255 --> 00:18:52,381
Itu saja. Jadi…

287
00:18:53,298 --> 00:18:58,011
Apa pendapat kamu?
Ada apa-apa idea atau pandangan?

288
00:18:58,095 --> 00:18:59,513
Tak ada idea yang buruk.

289
00:19:01,140 --> 00:19:03,433
Saya rasa rancangan itu hebat.

290
00:19:04,476 --> 00:19:06,812
Rancangan itu hebat, bukan?

291
00:19:06,895 --> 00:19:07,813
Hei.

292
00:19:09,231 --> 00:19:10,899
Ya, betul. Memang…

293
00:19:11,567 --> 00:19:12,818
Rancangan itu hebat.

294
00:19:12,901 --> 00:19:14,153
Cuma…

295
00:19:14,236 --> 00:19:15,320
Cuma…

296
00:19:15,404 --> 00:19:17,906
Will, awak bunuh Demo dengan minda awak?

297
00:19:17,990 --> 00:19:19,491
- Saya…
- Tiga Demo.

298
00:19:19,575 --> 00:19:20,784
Sekali gus.

299
00:19:20,868 --> 00:19:23,036
Biar betul sampai begitu sekali?

300
00:19:23,120 --> 00:19:24,413
Ahli jampi sebenar.

301
00:19:24,496 --> 00:19:26,582
Sebenarnya ahli sihir. Kuasa dia…

302
00:19:26,665 --> 00:19:27,916
Semula jadi. Ya.

303
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:28,917
Apa pentingnya?

304
00:19:29,001 --> 00:19:30,127
Pentinglah.

305
00:19:30,210 --> 00:19:32,462
Boleh tolong fokus tak?

306
00:19:33,130 --> 00:19:34,798
Okey, biar saya mula.

307
00:19:37,217 --> 00:19:41,054
Kita boleh bina satu lagi alat telemetri.

308
00:19:41,138 --> 00:19:45,976
Kemudian kita boleh cari El,
Jonathan dan yang lain.

309
00:19:46,059 --> 00:19:47,978
Harap mereka dapat jejak Vecna.

310
00:19:48,061 --> 00:19:51,732
Dustin yang bina penjejak itu.
Saya tak tahu caranya.

311
00:19:51,815 --> 00:19:55,277
Kita boleh fikir sama-sama,
tapi mungkin akan ambil masa…

312
00:19:55,360 --> 00:19:57,154
Berhari-hari. Tak sempat.

313
00:19:57,237 --> 00:20:00,991
Apa kata kita letak Will di belakang van
dan jadikan dia antena?

314
00:20:01,074 --> 00:20:02,743
- Apa?
- Tak ada idea buruk.

315
00:20:02,826 --> 00:20:04,328
Okey, apa lagi?

316
00:20:04,912 --> 00:20:06,663
Fikirlah. Apa lagi?

317
00:20:06,747 --> 00:20:07,915
Apa-apa saja.

318
00:20:08,749 --> 00:20:09,708
Apa-apa saja.

319
00:20:10,751 --> 00:20:12,127
Siapa lagi kebulur?

320
00:20:22,638 --> 00:20:23,639
Bugles?

321
00:20:23,722 --> 00:20:25,265
Dunia dah nak kiamat.

322
00:20:25,349 --> 00:20:26,475
Sebab itulah.

323
00:20:26,558 --> 00:20:29,895
Minda perlukan tenaga dan khasiat
untuk kekalkan fokus dan kreativiti.

324
00:20:31,605 --> 00:20:32,439
Makanlah.

325
00:20:50,207 --> 00:20:52,334
WSQK MENGALU-ALUKAN KELAB AV HAWKINS

326
00:21:02,886 --> 00:21:05,264
- Saya tahu!
- Saya tahu!

327
00:21:05,347 --> 00:21:06,932
Okey, saya cakap dulu.

328
00:21:07,015 --> 00:21:09,059
Dustin tak ada di sini,

329
00:21:09,142 --> 00:21:11,812
tapi mentor dia ada.

330
00:21:11,895 --> 00:21:14,356
- En. Clarke?
- Nerda terhebat di Hawkins.

331
00:21:14,439 --> 00:21:16,233
Dia ajar Dustin semuanya.

332
00:21:16,316 --> 00:21:19,486
Mesti dia boleh bina penjejak
dalam masa yang singkat.

333
00:21:19,569 --> 00:21:20,946
Mungkin menjadi.

334
00:21:21,029 --> 00:21:23,699
Ya, tapi ia akan mengambil masa.

335
00:21:23,782 --> 00:21:27,327
Rancangan saya lebih cepat,
lebih berani dan lebih baik.

336
00:21:28,453 --> 00:21:31,915
Waktu panaskan bertih jagung,
saya teringat Billy di sauna.

337
00:21:31,999 --> 00:21:35,627
Kita panaskan dia
untuk aktifkan zarah, bukan?

338
00:21:35,711 --> 00:21:38,547
Ia dorman macam biji jagung ini,

339
00:21:38,630 --> 00:21:41,675
macam zarah dalam badan Demo
yang Will dah bunuh.

340
00:21:41,758 --> 00:21:43,844
Panaskan saja untuk hidupkan balik.

341
00:21:43,927 --> 00:21:46,805
Kuasa 50,000 watt mengalir
melalui menara itu.

342
00:21:48,557 --> 00:21:52,185
Renjat bangkai Demo dengan elektrik
sampai mereka hidup balik.

343
00:21:52,269 --> 00:21:53,478
Kemudian selesailah,

344
00:21:53,562 --> 00:21:56,440
terus ada minda sarang untuk kita guna.

345
00:21:56,523 --> 00:22:00,068
Kau nak hidupkan Demo macam Frankenstein?
Itu idea hebat kau?

346
00:22:00,152 --> 00:22:02,571
- Rancangan kau lembap.
- Rancangan kau bodoh.

347
00:22:02,654 --> 00:22:04,489
Hei, anak-anak. Cukuplah itu!

348
00:22:04,573 --> 00:22:05,866
Tolong faham.

349
00:22:05,949 --> 00:22:09,578
Dua-dua ada kekurangan.
Banyak kekurangannya.

350
00:22:09,661 --> 00:22:11,288
Jadi, kita cuba dua-dua.

351
00:22:11,955 --> 00:22:14,875
Baling dua damak
dan harap satu mengena sasaran.

352
00:22:29,473 --> 00:22:31,850
Okey, banyaknya tangga.

353
00:22:33,101 --> 00:22:36,521
Khazanah tersembunyi
di kawasan kurungan yang paling dalam.

354
00:22:38,315 --> 00:22:41,568
Khazanah atau penjana perisai sihir?

355
00:22:41,651 --> 00:22:43,779
Janganlah ubah-ubah metafora.

356
00:22:44,321 --> 00:22:45,280
Analogi.

357
00:22:55,999 --> 00:22:57,125
Okey.

358
00:22:57,751 --> 00:23:01,338
Tak sangka ada taska
di tempat jahanam ini.

359
00:23:01,421 --> 00:23:02,547
Itu satu kelebihan.

360
00:23:04,591 --> 00:23:06,468
Gilalah, Henderson.

361
00:23:06,551 --> 00:23:07,594
Betul cakap kau.

362
00:23:11,098 --> 00:23:12,057
Khazanah.

363
00:23:14,643 --> 00:23:16,228
- Kau tahu tak?
- Apa?

364
00:23:16,311 --> 00:23:19,231
Kau sesuai di sini
sebab kematangan kau terbantut.

365
00:23:19,314 --> 00:23:20,816
Aku nak sambung cari.

366
00:23:20,899 --> 00:23:22,984
Kau duduklah gentel telur di sini.

367
00:23:23,068 --> 00:23:24,277
Bagus juga.

368
00:23:24,361 --> 00:23:26,863
- Yang ini aku setuju.
- Semestinya.

369
00:23:26,947 --> 00:23:29,533
Ya, semoga jumpa khazanah kau.

370
00:23:29,616 --> 00:23:30,992
Bukan, penjana perisai.

371
00:23:31,076 --> 00:23:32,786
Bukan, benda karut bodoh itu.

372
00:23:32,869 --> 00:23:33,870
Terima kasih.

373
00:23:34,579 --> 00:23:37,040
Saya risau kalau Dustin silap kali ini.

374
00:23:39,584 --> 00:23:41,420
Tempat ini dah mati.

375
00:23:42,879 --> 00:23:46,716
Entahlah. Makin lama,
makin nampak mustahil pula.

376
00:23:47,217 --> 00:23:48,718
Kita dah datang pun.

377
00:23:49,845 --> 00:23:51,721
Alang-alang, cari sajalah.

378
00:23:58,019 --> 00:23:58,895
Hei.

379
00:24:01,356 --> 00:24:02,774
Saya ada buat sesuatu

380
00:24:03,400 --> 00:24:05,444
yang buat awak bengang?

381
00:24:05,527 --> 00:24:07,154
Apa maksud awak?

382
00:24:07,237 --> 00:24:08,613
Entah. Nada suara awak.

383
00:24:08,697 --> 00:24:10,073
- Nada suara?
- Ya.

384
00:24:10,157 --> 00:24:12,909
- Okey.
- Nampak? Nada suara itulah.

385
00:24:12,993 --> 00:24:18,248
Ya, nada suara saya macam itu
sebab awak tiba-tiba merepek.

386
00:24:19,583 --> 00:24:22,544
Ya, di bawah tadi pun saya merepek?

387
00:24:22,627 --> 00:24:26,506
Maksud awak, waktu awak dan Steve
mula nak berlagak maco lagi?

388
00:24:26,590 --> 00:24:31,052
Tak, waktu Steve ajak awak ikut dia,
dan awak teragak-agak.

389
00:24:31,136 --> 00:24:34,598
Sebenarnya, saya cakap
kita patut ikut pasukan biasa.

390
00:24:35,223 --> 00:24:36,933
Ya, tapi awak teragak-agak.

391
00:24:37,017 --> 00:24:38,351
Saya tak teragak-agak.

392
00:24:38,435 --> 00:24:40,187
Saya kenal awak. Awak teragak-agak.

393
00:24:41,396 --> 00:24:44,399
Okey. Saya tak teragak-agak,
tapi kalau betul pun?

394
00:24:44,483 --> 00:24:46,109
Itu tak penting.

395
00:24:46,193 --> 00:24:48,111
Adik saya hilang.

396
00:24:48,195 --> 00:24:50,822
Ya, sebab itulah ia penting.

397
00:24:51,490 --> 00:24:53,867
Selepas semua benda yang dah berlaku,

398
00:24:53,950 --> 00:24:55,285
yang tengah berlaku,

399
00:24:55,368 --> 00:24:57,579
saya takut, Nancy.

400
00:24:57,662 --> 00:24:59,414
Saya betul-betul takut.

401
00:24:59,498 --> 00:25:02,501
Saya tak tahu apa yang menanti kita.

402
00:25:02,584 --> 00:25:04,127
Yang saya tahu,

403
00:25:04,211 --> 00:25:06,963
kalau kita nak ada peluang untuk selamat,

404
00:25:07,047 --> 00:25:08,757
kita perlu jadi satu pasukan.

405
00:25:08,840 --> 00:25:10,383
Pasukan macam dulu-dulu.

406
00:25:10,467 --> 00:25:13,136
Kita masih satu pasukan.

407
00:25:13,220 --> 00:25:14,054
Tak.

408
00:25:15,222 --> 00:25:16,306
Sekarang tak lagi.

409
00:25:16,389 --> 00:25:20,769
Jadi, awak nak selesaikan
semua masalah hubungan kita di sini?

410
00:25:20,852 --> 00:25:24,231
- Di Makmal Hawkins? Tempat Terbalik?
- Tak. Tak, Nancy.

411
00:25:24,314 --> 00:25:27,359
Saya cuma nak awak
berhenti lari daripada saya.

412
00:25:28,109 --> 00:25:29,528
Mula jujur dengan saya.

413
00:25:30,111 --> 00:25:31,530
Awak begitu selama ini?

414
00:25:32,614 --> 00:25:33,698
Jujur dengan saya?

415
00:25:35,450 --> 00:25:36,660
Ya.

416
00:25:36,743 --> 00:25:38,954
Ya, saya jujur dengan awak.

417
00:25:39,037 --> 00:25:40,038
Awak teragak-agak.

418
00:25:40,121 --> 00:25:41,039
Taklah.

419
00:25:41,122 --> 00:25:44,501
Saya kenal awak, Jonathan.
Jelas sangat awak teragak-agak.

420
00:26:39,097 --> 00:26:40,557
Awak buat apa?

421
00:26:41,224 --> 00:26:42,183
Jonathan!

422
00:26:45,979 --> 00:26:47,230
Apa benda ini?

423
00:26:48,064 --> 00:26:49,608
Apa itu?

424
00:26:50,609 --> 00:26:53,862
Dah terlambatkah
untuk saya setuju dengan teori Dustin?

425
00:27:01,703 --> 00:27:04,998
Nancy, Jonathan, dengar tak? Over.

426
00:27:06,082 --> 00:27:10,128
Kami dah sampai di gereja.
Kami tercari-cari kamu di mana.

427
00:27:10,211 --> 00:27:11,254
Dengar tak?

428
00:27:13,173 --> 00:27:14,215
Jonathan!

429
00:27:15,258 --> 00:27:17,010
Nancy, dengar tak?

430
00:27:18,219 --> 00:27:19,429
Tolonglah.

431
00:27:19,512 --> 00:27:22,057
Awak dan polis itu datang jauh-jauh.

432
00:27:22,724 --> 00:27:26,478
Mesti kamu terkejut
jumpa saya di situ, bukan Henry.

433
00:27:26,561 --> 00:27:27,937
Saya minta maaf, Kali.

434
00:27:28,813 --> 00:27:31,066
Maaf sebab tak jumpa awak lebih awal.

435
00:27:31,733 --> 00:27:33,026
Awak bukannya tahu.

436
00:27:33,109 --> 00:27:36,613
Saya ada tab mandi, tangki di rumah.

437
00:27:39,032 --> 00:27:41,368
Saya boleh cari jauh. Sini pun boleh.

438
00:27:42,577 --> 00:27:46,122
Rasanya saya takut nak cari awak.

439
00:27:47,207 --> 00:27:49,501
Setakat mana awak tahu tentang Henry?

440
00:27:49,584 --> 00:27:52,337
Semuanya, kecuali…

441
00:27:54,464 --> 00:27:56,424
dia masih hidup.

442
00:27:57,842 --> 00:27:59,260
Tolong saya cari dia,

443
00:28:00,595 --> 00:28:01,429
bunuh dia.

444
00:28:01,513 --> 00:28:02,472
Kemudian apa?

445
00:28:02,555 --> 00:28:03,765
Ia akan berakhir.

446
00:28:04,265 --> 00:28:06,935
Barulah kita boleh hidup.
Betul-betul hidup.

447
00:28:07,018 --> 00:28:08,520
Itu cuma angan-angan.

448
00:28:08,603 --> 00:28:10,105
Tak semestinya.

449
00:28:11,523 --> 00:28:14,734
Dulu saya pun ada angan-angan yang sama.

450
00:28:15,443 --> 00:28:17,696
Saya mampu hentikan semuanya.

451
00:28:19,364 --> 00:28:20,490
Saya mampu

452
00:28:22,325 --> 00:28:24,327
sembuhkan luka kita.

453
00:28:31,459 --> 00:28:32,836
Tapi mereka jumpa saya.

454
00:28:34,170 --> 00:28:35,797
Jumpa kawan-kawan saya.

455
00:28:35,880 --> 00:28:36,965
Tidak!

456
00:28:37,549 --> 00:28:38,508
Bunuh mereka.

457
00:28:40,093 --> 00:28:41,469
Mereka tahan saya.

458
00:29:25,013 --> 00:29:28,099
Saya tak faham
kenapa saya dibiarkan hidup.

459
00:29:28,183 --> 00:29:33,104
Saya ingat mungkin doktor itu ditugaskan
untuk menyeksa saya.

460
00:29:33,688 --> 00:29:35,440
Tapi ini bukan soal dendam.

461
00:29:36,274 --> 00:29:39,110
Dr. Kay perlukan saya.

462
00:29:39,194 --> 00:29:41,905
Dia perlukan darah saya.

463
00:29:42,781 --> 00:29:45,784
Keperluan dia tak berkesudahan.

464
00:29:50,872 --> 00:29:52,123
Dia terus ambil

465
00:29:53,374 --> 00:29:54,459
dan ambil lagi.

