Mereka akan cari awak
dan cipta lebih ramai orang macam awak!

700
00:46:43,050 --> 00:46:43,926
Macam Henry.

701
00:46:53,727 --> 00:46:55,521
Tak ada penamat gembira, Jane.

702
00:46:56,104 --> 00:46:57,397
Ia bukan untuk kita.

703
00:47:01,026 --> 00:47:03,278
Hei, tak apa. Ini saya.

704
00:47:04,112 --> 00:47:05,447
Ini saya.

705
00:47:30,764 --> 00:47:32,432
Barat laut.

706
00:47:33,809 --> 00:47:35,102
Sesat jalan, ya?

707
00:47:49,825 --> 00:47:51,159
Siapa beri peta ini?

708
00:47:51,243 --> 00:47:52,744
Mak kau!

709
00:47:52,828 --> 00:47:53,996
Pandang aku!

710
00:47:54,997 --> 00:47:56,790
Kalau kau tipu aku lagi,

711
00:47:57,624 --> 00:48:02,379
aku akan bunuh bapak kau yang bodoh…

712
00:48:04,715 --> 00:48:07,384
mak kau yang celaka…

713
00:48:10,304 --> 00:48:14,141
dan kakak kau yang sial.

714
00:48:18,270 --> 00:48:20,480
Baiklah, sayang. Masa main dah tamat.

715
00:48:21,732 --> 00:48:22,608
Mari masuk.

716
00:48:23,233 --> 00:48:25,319
Kenapa masam saja muka?

717
00:48:25,402 --> 00:48:31,617
Marilah, kita nak baca buku,
hasilkan seni dan belajar macam-macam.

718
00:48:34,745 --> 00:48:36,246
Betul tiada apa berlaku

719
00:48:36,330 --> 00:48:37,956
- sebelum Demo muncul?
- Ya.

720
00:48:38,040 --> 00:48:39,750
Cerita balik dari awal.

721
00:48:39,833 --> 00:48:41,668
- Dah cerita.
- Cerita lagi.

722
00:48:44,087 --> 00:48:46,548
Saya dan Mary di bulatan pusing.

723
00:48:47,132 --> 00:48:49,509
- Derek, janganlah!
- Pegang kuat-kuat!

724
00:48:49,593 --> 00:48:54,181
Derek buat perangai bangang macam biasa,
kemudian Henry panggil saya di sana.

725
00:48:54,264 --> 00:48:56,391
Dia kata dia nak lindungi saya.

726
00:48:56,475 --> 00:48:59,186
Saya tak jumpa dia lagi
sampai di padang itu.

727
00:48:59,269 --> 00:49:01,772
Saya dipanggil sebab ada kawan khayalan,

728
00:49:01,855 --> 00:49:05,817
kemudian mak berkelakuan pelik
dan bergaduh besar dengan ayah.

729
00:49:17,079 --> 00:49:18,080
Kenapa?

730
00:49:18,163 --> 00:49:20,666
Ada yang tak kena. Ia sepatutnya kuning.

731
00:49:20,749 --> 00:49:21,750
Berhenti!

732
00:49:39,184 --> 00:49:41,687
Mak!

733
00:49:41,770 --> 00:49:43,188
Mak! Ayah!

734
00:49:43,271 --> 00:49:46,233
Tolong! Tolong lepaskan aku!

735
00:49:47,901 --> 00:49:50,445
Mak!

736
00:49:50,529 --> 00:49:54,408
Tolong! Tolong, mak! Mak! Ayah!

737
00:49:57,786 --> 00:49:58,704
Ke belakang!

738
00:49:59,538 --> 00:50:00,956
Holly.

739
00:50:02,040 --> 00:50:03,417
Awak okey tak?

740
00:50:05,085 --> 00:50:06,503
Saya pun tak tahulah.

741
00:50:07,337 --> 00:50:08,338
Entah. Saya rasa…

742
00:50:08,422 --> 00:50:09,756
Takut?

743
00:50:09,840 --> 00:50:11,633
Memori terakhir dah dekat.

744
00:50:13,218 --> 00:50:16,346
Awak mungkin akan mula rasa sesuatu,

745
00:50:16,430 --> 00:50:18,348
perasaan awak pada malam itu.

746
00:50:19,599 --> 00:50:20,767
Saya pun alaminya.

747
00:50:22,853 --> 00:50:25,147
Tapi ia cuma macam gema.

748
00:50:25,814 --> 00:50:26,982
Itu petanda baik.

749
00:50:27,858 --> 00:50:29,818
Maknanya awak hampir boleh balik.

750
00:50:35,032 --> 00:50:36,658
Marilah. Ikut saya.

751
00:50:45,083 --> 00:50:47,711
Awak kata saya hampir boleh balik.

752
00:50:49,171 --> 00:50:51,298
Tapi awak akan ikut sekali, bukan?

753
00:50:52,340 --> 00:50:54,384
Tak. Saya nak tinggal di sini.

754
00:50:54,968 --> 00:50:57,179
Mestilah. Awak biar betul?

755
00:50:57,262 --> 00:50:58,138
Jom.

756
00:51:03,143 --> 00:51:04,519
- Hei!
- Apa kamu buat?

757
00:51:04,603 --> 00:51:05,937
Kabel tak jejak tanah.

758
00:51:06,021 --> 00:51:08,857
Kita kena buat eksperimen sains di atas.

759
00:51:15,572 --> 00:51:16,865
Okey.

760
00:51:16,948 --> 00:51:17,908
Perlahan-lahan.

761
00:51:20,243 --> 00:51:21,203
Okey.

762
00:51:23,413 --> 00:51:25,332
- Sedia? Sedia?
- Ya.

763
00:51:25,415 --> 00:51:26,708
Sedia!

764
00:51:48,355 --> 00:51:49,898
Okey, kita dah sedia.

765
00:51:55,695 --> 00:51:58,115
Kalau ada apa-apa jadi, keluar saja.

766
00:51:58,198 --> 00:51:59,866
Baik. Saya janji.

767
00:51:59,950 --> 00:52:02,953
Kalau keadaan jadi kacau,
kami akan naikkan voltan

768
00:52:03,036 --> 00:52:06,039
agar zarah rentung
dan putuskan dia daripada minda.

769
00:52:08,625 --> 00:52:10,293
- Mak?
- Ya?

770
00:52:10,877 --> 00:52:12,671
Terima kasih sebab percayakan saya.

771
00:52:15,048 --> 00:52:16,508
Bunuh bangsat itu.

772
00:52:17,884 --> 00:52:19,386
Baiklah. Kau boleh buat.

773
00:52:23,348 --> 00:52:24,808
Hidupkan, Frankenstein.

774
00:52:24,891 --> 00:52:26,685
Sebutannya "Fronkensteen"!

775
00:53:07,184 --> 00:53:10,145
Berkesan. Berkesan!

776
00:53:10,228 --> 00:53:11,730
Parasnya 50 peratus!

777
00:53:16,067 --> 00:53:17,027
Tolonglah.

778
00:53:42,093 --> 00:53:42,928
Bangang!

779
00:53:44,679 --> 00:53:46,765
Mana dia? Mana En. Whatsit?

780
00:53:46,848 --> 00:53:48,266
Rasanya aku Derek.

781
00:53:49,142 --> 00:53:51,645
- Derek?
- Dia ada bersama mereka.

782
00:53:52,562 --> 00:53:53,980
Budak-budak hilang itu.

783
00:53:54,064 --> 00:53:55,023
Holly pula?

784
00:53:55,607 --> 00:53:57,442
- Kau nampak Holly?
- Tak.

785
00:53:57,525 --> 00:54:01,655
Cepatlah jawab, bangang! Mana En. Whatsit?

786
00:54:01,738 --> 00:54:03,323
Cari Holly.

787
00:54:03,406 --> 00:54:06,952
Henry tengah cari dia.

788
00:54:07,035 --> 00:54:10,038
Holly takkan lari.
Dia tak macam itu. Kau tipu.

789
00:54:10,121 --> 00:54:12,874
Aku tak tipulah.
Ada raksasa perdayakan dia.

790
00:54:12,958 --> 00:54:16,461
Ia menyamar jadi perempuan
berbaju pelik dan berambut merah.

791
00:54:16,544 --> 00:54:17,379
Nama dia…

792
00:54:17,462 --> 00:54:18,296
Max.

793
00:54:18,380 --> 00:54:20,090
Sekejap. Kenapa dengan Max?

794
00:54:20,173 --> 00:54:21,216
Dia dengan Holly.

795
00:54:21,800 --> 00:54:24,594
Tapi Vecna tengah buru mereka.

796
00:54:35,855 --> 00:54:37,274
Saya tercegat saja.

797
00:54:38,775 --> 00:54:40,652
Kenapa saya tak tolong lawan?

798
00:54:40,735 --> 00:54:41,987
Itu Holly yang lama.

799
00:54:42,862 --> 00:54:43,738
Sekarang lain.

800
00:54:46,700 --> 00:54:49,953
Tidak! Mak! Mak, tolonglah!

801
00:54:50,787 --> 00:54:51,746
Jom.

802
00:55:13,685 --> 00:55:14,978
Apa itu?

803
00:55:16,354 --> 00:55:17,188
Jalan keluar.

804
00:55:17,772 --> 00:55:19,774
Tak nampak macam jalan keluar pun.

805
00:55:25,155 --> 00:55:27,073
Betulkah awak bukan raksasa?

806
00:55:27,907 --> 00:55:28,908
Betul.

807
00:55:37,667 --> 00:55:39,544
Aku dah pesan, Holly.

808
00:55:49,220 --> 00:55:50,972
Jangan masuk ke hutan.

809
00:55:55,643 --> 00:55:58,229
- Tak guna!
- Max, dia datang! Tidak!

810
00:55:58,313 --> 00:55:59,689
Holly, beri sini.

811
00:56:00,815 --> 00:56:02,359
Max, cepat!

812
00:56:29,677 --> 00:56:31,846
Akhirnya,

813
00:56:33,139 --> 00:56:35,642
si musang dah tertangkap.

814
00:56:36,643 --> 00:56:38,144
Berhenti!

815
00:56:51,825 --> 00:56:52,742
Max!

816
00:57:17,142 --> 00:57:18,393
Ia berkesan.

817
00:57:26,401 --> 00:57:27,277
Ahli sihir.

818
00:57:30,989 --> 00:57:32,907
Max! Awak tak apa-apa?

819
00:57:42,125 --> 00:57:43,751
- Max!
- Max!

820
00:57:43,835 --> 00:57:44,961
Kalau awak…

821
00:57:45,044 --> 00:57:48,006
…boleh dengar, tolong…

822
00:57:48,089 --> 00:57:50,175
- …lari…
- …sekarang!

823
00:57:51,468 --> 00:57:55,680
Lari!

824
00:58:18,119 --> 00:58:18,995
Keluar.

825
00:58:20,580 --> 00:58:21,748
Keluar!

826
00:58:22,957 --> 00:58:23,917
Keluar!

827
00:58:25,001 --> 00:58:26,461
Apa yang berlaku?

828
00:58:26,544 --> 00:58:27,504
Keluar!

829
00:58:28,588 --> 00:58:30,215
Keluar!

830
00:58:34,719 --> 00:58:36,513
- Will, dengar tak?
- Bangun!

831
00:58:36,596 --> 00:58:37,430
Mak ada.

832
00:58:37,514 --> 00:58:39,724
- Bangun, Will.
- Naikkan!

833
00:59:06,417 --> 00:59:07,961
Will, kembalilah.

834
00:59:08,044 --> 00:59:09,879
Kembalilah, Will. Will!

835
00:59:09,963 --> 00:59:11,881
- Tidak!
- Will, kembalilah!

836
00:59:11,965 --> 00:59:13,883
- Will!
- Kembalilah!

837
00:59:24,894 --> 00:59:26,771
Ada banyak benda cair ini lagi.

838
00:59:41,995 --> 00:59:42,996
Jonathan.

839
00:59:44,747 --> 00:59:45,790
Awak nampak tak?

840
00:59:47,917 --> 00:59:49,002
Apa?

841
00:59:49,877 --> 00:59:50,878
Lampu saya.

842
00:59:51,671 --> 00:59:52,672
Tengok.

843
01:00:09,981 --> 01:00:11,316
Ada sesuatu di sana.

844
01:00:44,432 --> 01:00:45,767
Sihir gelap.

845
01:00:49,020 --> 01:00:50,021
Ya Tuhan.

846
01:00:52,482 --> 01:00:54,442
Dustin, Steve, dengar tak?

847
01:00:54,525 --> 01:00:56,611
Kami jumpa penjana perisai. Dengar?

848
01:00:58,821 --> 01:01:00,782
Jonathan, ini Dustin. Dengar tak?

849
01:01:00,865 --> 01:01:04,994
Aku tak dengar. Kau dengar tak?
Kami dah jumpa penjana perisai itu.

850
01:01:05,078 --> 01:01:07,664
Dengar sini, okey? Jangan buat apa-apa.

851
01:01:07,747 --> 01:01:08,873
Jangan usik!

852
01:01:08,956 --> 01:01:10,208
Jangan usik apa-apa!

853
01:01:10,792 --> 01:01:11,668
Alamak!

854
01:01:16,964 --> 01:01:18,508
Mereka di luar lingkungan.

855
01:01:20,468 --> 01:01:23,262
Nampaknya, tak dapatlah mereka tengok.

856
01:01:37,235 --> 01:01:38,069
Jonathan!

857
01:01:39,404 --> 01:01:41,572
Kalau kau boleh dengar, aku silap!

858
01:01:41,656 --> 01:01:44,784
Itu sebenarnya bukan penjana perisai!

859
01:01:45,368 --> 01:01:48,121
Ia bukan sihir gelap, tapi benda lain!

860
01:01:48,204 --> 01:01:50,081
Jonathan! Nancy!

861
01:01:53,334 --> 01:01:55,002
Jonathan! Nancy!

862
01:01:55,086 --> 01:01:57,797
Kalau kamu hancurkannya, kamu akan mati!

863
01:01:57,880 --> 01:01:58,881
Kita akan mati!

864
01:01:58,965 --> 01:02:01,342
Holly akan mati! Semua orang akan mati!

865
01:02:01,426 --> 01:02:03,010
Boleh dengar tak?

866
01:02:05,263 --> 01:02:06,389
Awak yakinkah?

867
01:02:09,559 --> 01:02:10,518
Tak.

868
01:04:46,465 --> 01:04:50,887
Terjemahan sari kata oleh M Arrazi Azmi

